to-33-months-in-prison-for-part-in-mass-brawl-3359757">被判入狱 33 个月</a>，此前他因持有瓶子作为攻击性武器而被判入狱 33 个月，并在他的朋友 Fidel Glasgow（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/the-specials">The Specials 成员</a>Neville Staple 的孙子） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pa-salieu-charged-in-connection-with-fidel-glasgow-case-2912784">被刺伤后爆发斗殴事件后</a>，又被判犯有暴力骚乱罪。 2018年。</p><p>然而，21 个月后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pa-salieu-released-from-prison-and-teases-new-music-3790200">Salieu 宣布回归</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pa-salieu-drops-first-new-music-since-prison-release-with-hopeful-single-belly-3791370">推出了他入狱以来的第一首新歌《Belly》</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosures-london-boiler-room-set-cancelled-due-to-crowd-surge-3787980">Disclosure 的伦敦锅炉房演出最近由于人群激增而被取消</a>。</p><p> Post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/disclosure-and-pa-salieu-team-up-for-cold-new-collaboration-king-steps-3816725">Disclosure 和 Pa Salieu 联手推出冷酷新合作歌曲“King Steps”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
尼克·卡特针对强奸原告的诽谤诉讼获得法官批准https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carters-defamation-lawsuit-against-rape-accuser-to-be-allowed-by-judge-3816718?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-carters-法官允许针对强奸原告提起诽谤诉讼Liberty DunworthThu, 28 Nov 2024 10:10:16 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3816718 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·卡特，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他被指控在 2001 年对一名 17 岁的粉丝进行性侵犯</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carters-defamation-lawsuit-against-rape-accuser-to-be-allowed-by-judge-3816718">尼克·卡特针对强奸原告的诽谤诉讼获得法官批准的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·卡特，2024" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>法官在新裁决中称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-carter">尼克·卡特</a>针对强奸原告的诽谤诉讼可以继续推进。</p><p>内华达州法官周二（11 月 26 日）裁定，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/backstreet-boys">后街男孩</a>歌手可以对香农·“谢伊”·露丝提起反诉，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-accused-of-raping-17-year-old-fan-in-2001-3363992">于 2022 年提起民事诉讼，指控这位歌手于 2001 年在巡演巴士上强奸了她，当时她当时17岁。</a></p><p>露丝声称卡特递给她一杯饮料，她认为其中含有酸果蔓汁和酒精的混合物，然后在公交车上袭击了她。她补充说，所谓的事件发生时，他在一场音乐会后从一群寻求签名的歌迷中挑选了她。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-responds-rape-allegations-melissa-schuman-2162331">卡特一再否认所有指控</a>，而他的律师则称这些指控“在法律上毫无依据”且“完全不真实”。他继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-files-countersuit-against-rape-accuser-3391785">对露丝提起反诉讼</a>，指控她诽谤。</p><p>现在，根据<a href="https://people.com/nevada-supreme-court-denies-appeal-by-accuser-to-dismiss-nick-carter-counterclaim-8753013" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>获得的文件，内华达州最高法院法官南希·阿尔夫（Nancy L. Allf）裁定，露丝针对卡特反诉提出的反SLAPP动议已被驳回，因为她“未能履行自己的负担”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784082" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784082" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784082" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784082" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·卡特 (Nick Carter) 将于 2024 年登台表演。图片来源：Iwi Onodera/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>文件中写道：“我们对这一上诉的解决受到了阻碍，因为露丝未能具体识别构成露丝反 SLAPP 动议基础的任何陈述。” “因此，我们的结论是，卡特反诉所依据的任何陈述，如果本命令中没有具体提及，都不能保证推翻地方法院的命令。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judge-rules-nick-carter-can-countersue-rape-accuser-3424209">2023 年 3 月也做出了类似的裁决</a>，当时法官确认卡特可以对露丝提起反诉讼。</p><p>除了露丝的指控外，卡特还被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-sued-for-sexual-assault-by-dreams-melissa-schuman-3429104">指控袭击了 Dream 乐队前成员梅丽莎·舒曼 (Melissa Schuman)</a> ，她最初于 2017 年向警方提交了报告。尼克对这些指控做出了回应，称他“感到震惊和悲伤”，因为他相信他们的遭遇是“双方同意的”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-files-countersuit-against-rape-accuser-3391785">尼克以诽谤罪对露丝和舒曼提出反诉</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/backstreet-boys-nick-carter-faces-third-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3491442">第三名姓名缩写 AR 的原告也于 2023 年起诉了这位歌手，</a>在拉斯维加斯提起诉讼，声称尼克在她 15 岁时强奸了她。她声称这些事件多次发生在一艘游艇上，一次发生在一辆旅游巴士的后面。据<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/nick-carter-third-sexual-assault-lawsuit-filed-1235403404/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard 报道，</a></em> 2003 年，卡特 23 岁。</p><p>当时，卡特的律师小戴尔·海耶斯(Dale Hayes Jr)发表了一份声明，其中写道：“在新的法律诉讼中重复同样的虚假指控并不会让它们变得更加真实。尼克期待着证据的出现以及这些恶意计划的真相曝光。” </p><figure id="attachment_3784080" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784080" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784080" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="尼克·卡特 2024 年登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Nick-Carter-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784080" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·卡特 (Nick Carter) 将于 2024 年登台表演。图片来源：Iwi Onodera/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>至于他对露丝的反诉，卡特提供了反驳她的主张的证据。包括后街男孩保安在内的几名目击者声称，演唱会结束后，乐队很快回到了西雅图的四季酒店，据称露丝当时正在排队等待签名。他的团队还声称不存在这样的线。</p><p>文件称：“任何歌迷都不可能与任何乐队成员单独坐在旅游巴士上。”</p><p>乐队和卡特当时的朋友苏珊·里格斯此前作证说，她“亲眼看到卡特离开场地，登上他的旅游巴士，然后立即开车离开。”此外，参加演出前见面会的粉丝 Ashley Large 声称演出结束后没有签名行（据<em>《人物</em>》报道）。</p><p>这是一个发展的故事。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-hits-back-at-outrageous-sexual-assault-claims-3761061"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、攻击和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carters-defamation-lawsuit-against-rape-accuser-to-be-allowed-by-judge-3816718">尼克·卡特针对强奸原告的诽谤诉讼获得法官批准的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
