 《泰德·拉索》明星证实了流行的粉丝理论，即它的灵感来自《绿野仙踪》 https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ted-lasso-star-confirms-popular-fan-theory-that-it-was-inspired-by-the-wizard-of-oz-3816679?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ted-lasso-star-confirms-popular-fan-theory-that-it-was-inspired-by-the-wizard-of-ozSurej Singh Thu, 28 Nov 2024 06:15:50 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3816679 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我是铁皮人，特德是多萝西”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ted-lasso-star-confirms-popular-fan-theory-that-it-was-inspired-by-the-wizard-of-oz-3816679">《泰德·拉索》的主演证实了流行的粉丝理论，即它的灵感来自《绿野仙踪》，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/brett-goldstein-lasso@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont